_sText:
This is my First actual FPS map that I really want to share with and improve, which to me is crazy because i'd usually have an idea but right in the beginning i'd give up.

Currently I'd say that It's half way done. I'd love to improve it's style some more and optimize the map.

Features:
  • Buyzones
  • 2 Bombs sites
  • Sniper / scouting Spots
  • HDR
  • Cubemaps (first load a map like italy in order for it to work)
  • Lots of crates

I would love some feedback.
